name: Pink Daisies Anklet
description:
I made this gorgeous anklet with one of my favorite weaves, daisy. Each “daisy” and it’s connector rings are 16 gauge sterling silver. 9 swarovksi 4mm fuchsia cubes dangle from handmade and wrapped fine silver headpins. It’s sexy and fun!

	The anklet length is approximately 10 inches, but it can be sized as needed. Please let me know after purchase with sizing requirements.
